        content: "Funcții de ranking — atribuie numere de ordine rândurilor.\n\nROW_NUMBER — număr unic, continuu:\n```sql\nSELECT \n    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY total DESC) AS pozitie,\n    client,\n    total\nFROM comenzi;\n-- 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 ... fără duplicate\n\n-- ROW_NUMBER per grup (top 3 produse per categorie):\nSELECT * FROM (\n    SELECT \n        *,\n        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY categorie ORDER BY pret DESC) AS rn\n    FROM produse\n) t\nWHERE rn <= 3; -- Primele 3 produse per categorie\n```\n\nRANK — cu \"goluri\" la duplicate:\n```sql\nSELECT \n    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY punctaj DESC) AS clasament,\n    jucator,\n    punctaj\nFROM scoruri;\n-- Rezultat:\n-- 1, Ana, 100\n-- 2, Bob, 90\n-- 2, Cara, 90  -- Loc 2 (la egal cu Bob)\n-- 4, Dan, 80   -- Loc 4 (sare 3!)\n```\n\nDENSE_RANK — fără goluri:\n```sql\nSELECT \n    DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY punctaj DESC) AS clasament,\n    jucator,\n    punctaj\nFROM scoruri;\n-- 1, Ana, 100\n-- 2, Bob, 90\n-- 2, Cara, 90   -- Loc 2\n-- 3, Dan, 80    -- Loc 3 (nu 4!)\n```\n\nNTILE — împarte în N grupuri:\n```sql\nSELECT \n    NTILE(4) OVER (ORDER BY salariu DESC) AS quartila,\n    angajat,\n    salariu\nFROM angajati;\n-- Quartila 1 = top 25%, Quartila 4 = bottom 25%\n```",
