        content: "CTE-urile recursive pot parcurge structuri ierarhice: categorii, meniuri, organigramă, comentarii imbricate.\n\nSINTAXĂ RECURSIVĂ:\n```sql\nWITH RECURSIVE cte_name AS (\n    -- Ancore (punct de start — rânduri fără părinte):\n    SELECT id, nume, parinte_id, 0 AS nivel\n    FROM categorii\n    WHERE parinte_id IS NULL\n    \n    UNION ALL\n    \n    -- Pas recursiv (fiecare nivel):\n    SELECT c.id, c.nume, c.parinte_id, ct.nivel + 1\n    FROM categorii c\n    INNER JOIN cte_name ct ON c.parinte_id = ct.id\n)\nSELECT * FROM cte_name\nORDER BY nivel, id;\n```\n\nEXEMPLU REAL — organigramă angajați:\n```sql\nWITH RECURSIVE ierarhie AS (\n    -- CEO (fără manager):\n    SELECT id, nume, manager_id, 0 AS nivel, CAST(nume AS CHAR(500)) AS cale\n    FROM angajati\n    WHERE manager_id IS NULL\n    \n    UNION ALL\n    \n    -- Angajați cu manager:\n    SELECT a.id, a.nume, a.manager_id, i.nivel + 1,\n           CONCAT(i.cale, ' > ', a.nume)\n    FROM angajati a\n    INNER JOIN ierarhie i ON a.manager_id = i.id\n)\nSELECT \n    REPEAT('  ', nivel) AS indent,\n    id,\n    nume,\n    cale\nFROM ierarhie\nORDER BY cale;\n```\n\nPREVENȚIE CICLURI INFINITE:\n```sql\n-- Limiteaza adâncimea:\nWHERE nivel < 10  -- la final\n\n-- MySQL MAXRECURSION:\nSET SESSION cte_max_recursion_depth = 100;\n```",
